---
layout: base.njk
title: "Toutes les prestations atelier | RED-K MOTORS"
description: "Consultez toutes les prestations atelier RED-K MOTORS et accedez a chaque fiche detaillee."
pageKey: prestations
---

<section class="presta-listing" aria-labelledby="presta-listing-title">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 id="presta-listing-title">Toutes nos prestations atelier</h1>
    <p>Choisissez une prestation pour voir le detail, les points controles et les questions frequentes.</p>

    <div class="presta-listing__grid">
      {% for category in prestations.categories %}
      <article class="presta-listing__card">
        <h2>{{ category.title }}</h2>
        <ul>
          {% for service in category.services %}
          <li><a href="/prestations/{{ service.slug }}/">{{ service.name }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
